function Insured__Dynamic_Data__HeartCondition return Boolean type tpValue : .Boolean
var p : Boolean
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0, 7, 'Insured__Dynamic_Data__HeartCondition') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
function Insured__Dynamic_Data__Cancer return Boolean type tpValue : .Boolean
var p : Boolean
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(1, 7, 'Insured__Dynamic_Data__Cancer') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
function Insured__Dynamic_Data__Illness return Boolean type tpValue : .Boolean
var p : Boolean
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(2, 7, 'Insured__Dynamic_Data__Illness') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
function Insured__Dynamic_Data__MedicalAdvice return Boolean type tpValue : .Boolean
var p : Boolean
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(3, 7, 'Insured__Dynamic_Data__MedicalAdvice') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Boolean) Result = self.Insured__Dynamic_Data__HeartCondition or self.Insured__Dynamic_Data__Cancer or self.Insured__Dynamic_Data__Illness or self.Insured__Dynamic_Data__MedicalAdvice endProc
